Class SpaceAlarmGeoPoint

java.lang.Object
  com.spacealarm.SpaceAlarmGeoPoint

public class SpaceAlarmGeoPoint
extends java.lang.Object

This class allows for easy and consistent conversion of integer latitudes and longitudes to their double values and vice versa.
